import React from 'react';
import styled from 'styled-components';

const LogoContainer = styled.div`
  display: flex;
  align-items: center;
  gap: ${props => props.theme.spacing.sm};
  cursor: pointer;
  transition: ${props => props.theme.transitions.base};
  
  &:hover {
    transform: scale(1.05);
  }
`;

const LogoIcon = styled.div`
  width: ${props => props.size === 'large' ? '48px' : props.size === 'medium' ? '36px' : '28px'};
  height: ${props => props.size === 'large' ? '48px' : props.size === 'medium' ? '36px' : '28px'};
  position: relative;
  display: flex;
  align-items: center;
  justify-content: center;
`;

const LogoText = styled.span`
  font-family: ${props => props.theme.fonts.primary};
  font-weight: ${props => props.theme.fontWeights.bold};
  font-size: ${props => props.size === 'large' ? props.theme.fontSizes['2xl'] : 
                        props.size === 'medium' ? props.theme.fontSizes.xl : 
                        props.theme.fontSizes.lg};
  background: ${props => props.theme.colors.gradientPrimary};
  -webkit-background-clip: text;
  -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
  background-clip: text;
  letter-spacing: -0.02em;
`;

const LokanexLogo = ({ size = 'medium', showText = true, ...props }) => {
  return (
    <LogoContainer {...props}>
      <LogoIcon size={size}>
        <svg
          width="100%"
          height="100%"
          viewBox="0 0 100 100"
          fill="none"
          xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
        >
          {/* Outer dynamic ring */}
          <circle
            cx="50"
            cy="50"
            r="45"
            stroke="url(#outerRing)"
            strokeWidth="2"
            fill="none"
            strokeDasharray="6,3"
            opacity="0.8"
          />
          
          {/* Central L with modern twist */}
          <g transform="translate(50,50)">
            {/* Main L structure */}
            <rect x="-15" y="-15" width="6" height="30" fill="url(#lMain)" rx="2" />
            <rect x="-15" y="9" width="24" height="6" fill="url(#lMain)" rx="2" />
            
            {/* Floating tech elements */}
            <circle cx="20" cy="-20" r="3" fill="url(#tech1)" />
            <rect x="25" y="15" width="4" height="4" fill="url(#tech2)" rx="1" />
            <polygon points="-25,-25 -20,-25 -22.5,-20" fill="url(#tech3)" />
          </g>
          
          {/* Data flow connections */}
          <path d="M35 30 Q50 20 65 30" stroke="url(#flow1)" strokeWidth="2" fill="none" opacity="0.6" />
          <path d="M65 70 Q50 80 35 70" stroke="url(#flow2)" strokeWidth="2" fill="none" opacity="0.6" />
          <path d="M30 35 Q20 50 30 65" stroke="url(#flow3)" strokeWidth="2" fill="none" opacity="0.6" />
          <path d="M70 65 Q80 50 70 35" stroke="url(#flow4)" strokeWidth="2" fill="none" opacity="0.6" />
          
          {/* Central glow */}
          <circle cx="50" cy="50" r="20" fill="url(#centerGlow)" opacity="0.4" />
          
          {/* Corner nodes */}
          <circle cx="20" cy="20" r="2" fill="url(#node1)" />
          <circle cx="80" cy="20" r="2" fill="url(#node2)" />
          <circle cx="20" cy="80" r="2" fill="url(#node3)" />
          <circle cx="80" cy="80" r="2" fill="url(#node4)" />
          
          {/* Floating particles */}
          <circle cx="15" cy="50" r="1.5" fill="url(#particle1)" opacity="0.7" />
          <circle cx="85" cy="50" r="1.5" fill="url(#particle2)" opacity="0.7" />
          <circle cx="50" cy="15" r="1.5" fill="url(#particle3)" opacity="0.7" />
          <circle cx="50" cy="85" r="1.5" fill="url(#particle4)" opacity="0.7" />
          
          {/* Gradients */}
          <defs>
            <linearGradient id="outerRing" x1="0%" y1="0%" x2="100%" y2="100%">
              <stop offset="0%" stopColor="#00d4ff" />
              <stop offset="25%" stopColor="#4ecdc4" />
              <stop offset="50%" stopColor="#ff6b35" />
              <stop offset="75%" stopColor="#4ecdc4" />
              <stop offset="100%" stopColor="#00d4ff" />
            </linearGradient>
            <linearGradient id="lMain" x1="0%" y1="0%" x2="100%" y2="100%">
              <stop offset="0%" stopColor="#ffffff" />
              <stop offset="30%" stopColor="#00d4ff" />
              <stop offset="70%" stopColor="#4ecdc4" />
              <stop offset="100%" stopColor="#0099cc" />
            </linearGradient>
            <radialGradient id="tech1" cx="50%" cy="50%" r="50%">
              <stop offset="0%" stopColor="#ff6b35" />
              <stop offset="100%" stopColor="#ff8c42" />
            </radialGradient>
            <radialGradient id="tech2" cx="50%" cy="50%" r="50%">
              <stop offset="0%" stopColor="#4ecdc4" />
              <stop offset="100%" stopColor="#44a08d" />
            </radialGradient>
            <radialGradient id="tech3" cx="50%" cy="50%" r="50%">
              <stop offset="0%" stopColor="#00d4ff" />
              <stop offset="100%" stopColor="#0099cc" />
            </radialGradient>
            <linearGradient id="flow1" x1="0%" y1="0%" x2="100%" y2="0%">
              <stop offset="0%" stopColor="#00d4ff" />
              <stop offset="100%" stopColor="#ff6b35" />
            </linearGradient>
            <linearGradient id="flow2" x1="0%" y1="0%" x2="100%" y2="0%">
              <stop offset="0%" stopColor="#ff6b35" />
              <stop offset="100%" stopColor="#4ecdc4" />
            </linearGradient>
            <linearGradient id="flow3" x1="0%" y1="0%" x2="0%" y2="100%">
              <stop offset="0%" stopColor="#4ecdc4" />
              <stop offset="100%" stopColor="#00d4ff" />
            </linearGradient>
            <linearGradient id="flow4" x1="0%" y1="0%" x2="0%" y2="100%">
              <stop offset="0%" stopColor="#00d4ff" />
              <stop offset="100%" stopColor="#ff6b35" />
            </linearGradient>
            <radialGradient id="centerGlow" cx="50%" cy="50%" r="50%">
              <stop offset="0%" stopColor="#ffffff" stopOpacity="0.6" />
              <stop offset="70%" stopColor="#00d4ff" stopOpacity="0.3" />
              <stop offset="100%" stopColor="#4ecdc4" stopOpacity="0.1" />
            </radialGradient>
            <radialGradient id="node1" cx="50%" cy="50%" r="50%">
              <stop offset="0%" stopColor="#ff6b35" />
              <stop offset="100%" stopColor="#ff8c42" />
            </radialGradient>
            <radialGradient id="node2" cx="50%" cy="50%" r="50%">
              <stop offset="0%" stopColor="#4ecdc4" />
              <stop offset="100%" stopColor="#44a08d" />
            </radialGradient>
            <radialGradient id="node3" cx="50%" cy="50%" r="50%">
              <stop offset="0%" stopColor="#00d4ff" />
              <stop offset="100%" stopColor="#0099cc" />
            </radialGradient>
            <radialGradient id="node4" cx="50%" cy="50%" r="50%">
              <stop offset="0%" stopColor="#ff6b35" />
              <stop offset="100%" stopColor="#ff8c42" />
            </radialGradient>
            <radialGradient id="particle1" cx="50%" cy="50%" r="50%">
              <stop offset="0%" stopColor="#00d4ff" />
              <stop offset="100%" stopColor="#0099cc" />
            </radialGradient>
            <radialGradient id="particle2" cx="50%" cy="50%" r="50%">
              <stop offset="0%" stopColor="#4ecdc4" />
              <stop offset="100%" stopColor="#44a08d" />
            </radialGradient>
            <radialGradient id="particle3" cx="50%" cy="50%" r="50%">
              <stop offset="0%" stopColor="#ff6b35" />
              <stop offset="100%" stopColor="#ff8c42" />
            </radialGradient>
            <radialGradient id="particle4" cx="50%" cy="50%" r="50%">
              <stop offset="0%" stopColor="#00d4ff" />
              <stop offset="100%" stopColor="#0099cc" />
            </radialGradient>
          </defs>
        </svg>
      </LogoIcon>
      {showText && <LogoText size={size}>Lokanex</LogoText>}
    </LogoContainer>
  );
};

export default LokanexLogo;
